<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Whiz-MD Multi-Device Pairing</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to Whiz-MD Multi-Device Pairing</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Your seamless solution for connecting your WhatsApp account.</p>

        <div class="pairing-options">
            <div class="option-card">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-qrcode"></i> Pair with QR Code</h2>
                <p class="description">The standard and quickest way to link your device. Simply scan the QR code displayed using your WhatsApp application.</p>
                <a href="/qr" class="btn-select">Use QR Code</a>
            </div>

            <div class="option-card">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i> Pair with Phone Number</h2>
                <p class="description">Generate a unique code to link your WhatsApp account by entering your phone number. Ideal if you cannot use your camera or prefer a code-based method.</p>
                <a href="/pairing-code" class="btn-select">Use Pairing Code</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-info">
            <p>Whiz-MD &copy; 2024 - Streamlining your WhatsApp connections.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
